name: Sailor Venus
description: Guardian Venus is the guardian spirit of the Venus Crystal and Princess Venus. She is a Sailor Power Guardian who appears in the Dream arc of the manga and crystal.

description: 'I am the Pretty Guardian who fights for Love and for Courage. I am Sailor Jupiter! I'll make you feel regret, it'll leave you numb!'

name: Sailors Uranus, Pluto & Neptuno
description: Outer Sailor Guardians is a group of Sailor Guardians who defend the solar system from external threat. This role contrasts the Inner Sailor Senshi, who are designated to protect Princess Serenity. The 'Outer Sailor Guardians, Outer Sailor Senshi, Outer Sailor Soldiers, Outer Senshi,' and others are all terms coined by fans and are not official titles, however.'

name: Sailor Saturn
description: Guardian Saturn is the guardian spirit of the Saturn Crystal and Princess Saturn. She is a Sailor Power Guardian who appears in the Dream and Stars arcs of the manga and crystal.

name: Sailor Guardians
description: The Inner Sailor Guardians were the protectors of Princess Serenity in the Silver Millennium. They are typically referred to unofficially by fans as 'Inner Senshi,'Inner Soldiers', Inner Guardians, or Inner Sailor Senshi; however, they are never addressed by this in the series; the term was only coined to distinguish them from the Outer Senshi.'

name: Sailor Galaxy
description: Evil and destruction Sailor, wants to just teh power of the galaxy

name: Darien 'Prince Endymion'
description: Prince Endymion was the Prince of the Earth during the era of the Silver Millennium, and was the beloved of Princess Serenity. In the 20th century, he was reborn as Mamoru Chiba.

name: Luna
description: Luna is a talking black-purple cat that advises Usagi Tsukino/Sailor Moon and the rest of the Sailor Senshi through the anime series. This is the first anime depiction of the original manga character. Her counterpart is Artemis, who assists Sailor V.

name: Sailors Starlights
description: The 'Sailor Starlights' are a group of three Sailor Senshi who came to Earth in search of their princess, Kakyuu, after their home planet of Kinmoku was destroyed by Sailor Galaxia. They appear in the manga, 90's anime, crystal, and many Sera Myu.
